---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout>
    <section
            class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2A004E] via-[#500073] to-[#2A004E] flex items-center justify-center text-white">
        <div class="text-center max-w-4xl px-8">
            <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold mb-6 ">
                Repositorio completo.
            </h1>
            <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold mb-6 ">
                <span class="text-[#F14A00]">Al descubierto</span>.
            </h1>
            <p class="text-2xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
                Conecta tu repo de GitHub y obtén análisis automático en segundos
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
                Conoce tu repositorio completamente.
            </p>
            <a href="/analyze" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#C62300] to-[#F14A00]
            px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold
            hover:from-[#F14A00] hover:to-[#C62300] inline-block
            active:from-[#500073] active:to-[#C62300]">
                Analizar mi repo
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center">
        <ul class="text-center max-w-4xl grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <li class="p-6 mx-4 sm:mx-0 cursor-default select-none bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🚀</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-[#2A004E]">Análisis automático</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Conecta tu repo de GitHub y obtén métricas en segundos</p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-6 mx-4 sm:mx-0 cursor-default select-none bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                <div class="text-3xl mb-4">📈</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-[#2A004E]">Insights avanzados</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Salud del proyecto, actividad de la comunidad, estructura del código y patrones
                    de desarrollo</p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-6 mx-4 sm:mx-0 cursor-default select-none bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                <div class="text-3xl mb-4">💸</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-[#2A004E]">Gratis</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Análisis ilimitados sin registro ni pagos</p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-6 mx-4 sm:mx-0 cursor-default select-none bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                <div class="text-3xl mb-4">⚙️</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-[#2A004E]">Transparente y libre</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Código fuente disponible, modifica y mejora</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section
            class="min-h-screen px-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2A004E] via-[#500073] to-[#2A004E]
            flex items-center justify-center flex-col text-white text-center">
        <p class="text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-14">Tu repositorio merece ser <span class="underline decoration-[#F14A00]">entendido</span>
        </p>
        <a href="/analyze" class="border-4 rounded-full border-white py-5 px-7
        bg-gradient-to-br from-[#F14A00] to-[#C62300] hover:animate-pulse hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">¿Listo para descubrirlo?</span>
        </a>
    </section>
</Layout>